text: Tan Xueqin is a Chinese taekwondo practitioner. She won a bronze medal in finweight at the 2019 World Taekwondo Championships, after being defeated by Mahla Momenzadeh in the semifinal. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Chinese female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
